videoSnippet.title: Stream Announcement - A Tournament for Subscribers, Challenges and some Chess Jokes
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator Just testing out my Phone camera to announce tomorrow's stream. In the video, I blundered and said the tournament will last 4 hours :D The tournament will last 1 hour and the stream will last 4 hours :)
Hope to see most of you in the stream :)

Tournament will be held on Lichess.org at 6 p.m. Croatian time.
